---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Verfix Documentation — Local-First Browser Verification for AI Agents"
  description="Docs for Verfix, the verifier in your AI coding agent's loop: CLI reference, config schema, execution modes, and config-first verification. No Docker required."
>
  <main class="docs-hub-hero">
    <div class="glow-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    
    <div class="hub-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="hub-header">
        <span class="hub-badge">DOCUMENTATION PORTAL</span>
        <h1 class="hub-title">The verifier in your agent's loop</h1>
        <p class="hub-subtitle">
          Everything for wiring Verfix into an AI coding agent's edit → verify → fix loop — CLI reference, config schema, execution modes, and the config-first guardrails that keep it from rewriting your app.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Quick Path / Featured -->
      <section class="quick-path">
        <div class="quick-card">
          <div class="quick-card-body">
            <span class="quick-label">GETTING STARTED</span>
            <h2>New to Verfix? Let's install the CLI</h2>
            <p>Install the CLI, run `verfix init`, and run your first browser verification flow in under 2 minutes — no Docker required.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/getting-started" class="quick-card-action">
            Start Setup
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Grid Sections -->
      <section class="hub-grid">
        <!-- Section: References -->
        <div class="hub-section-col">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <svg class="heading-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path>
              <path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h2>API & References</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="cards-stack">
            <a href="/cli-reference" class="hub-card">
              <h3>CLI Reference</h3>
              <p>Command reference manual for managing servers, initiating runs, and reviewing execution flows via standard shell scripts.</p>
              <span class="card-link">Read CLI guide →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/config-reference" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Config Reference</h3>
              <p>Complete configuration parameters for `verfix.config.json` including timeout settings, flow parameters, and system schemas.</p>
              <span class="card-link">See config specs →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section: Architecture & Core -->
        <div class="hub-section-col">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <svg class="heading-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line>
              <line x1="15" y1="3" x2="15" y2="21"></line>
              <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
              <line x1="3" y1="15" x2="21" y2="15"></line>
            </svg>
            <h2>Concepts & Architecture</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="cards-stack">
            <a href="/execution-modes" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Execution Modes</h3>
              <p>Learn the behaviors, guarantees, and trade-offs of the Strict, Assisted, and Exploratory execution strategies.</p>
              <span class="card-link">Understand run styles →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/failure-taxonomy" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Failure Taxonomy</h3>
              <p>Explore the full categorization of failure types, including visibility issues, selector errors, and structured hint layouts.</p>
              <span class="card-link">View taxomony schema →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section: Guides -->
        <div class="hub-section-col">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <svg class="heading-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h2>Developer Guides</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="cards-stack">
            <a href="/agent-integration" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Agent Integration</h3>
              <p>Step-by-step guides for connecting Verfix structured JSON feedback into LLM architectures, AutoGen, and LangChain environments.</p>
              <span class="card-link">Connect AI Agents →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/config-first-verification" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Config-First Verification</h3>
              <p>Why agents should fix flows, not rewrite your app, and the git-baseline source guard that enforces it.</p>
              <span class="card-link">Read the guide →</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/self-hosting" class="hub-card">
              <h3>Self-Hosting Guide (Optional)</h3>
              <p>The opt-in Docker server runtime — API, queue, and timeline dashboard — for teams that want a shared deployment.</p>
              <span class="card-link">Deploy to private servers →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>

<style>
  .docs-hub-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--vf-bg);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 120px 2rem 6rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .glow-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 350px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hub-container {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hub-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .hub-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--vf-green);
    background: rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.2);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hub-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--vf-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hub-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--vf-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Featured Quick Card */
  .quick-path {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .quick-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--vf-surface), rgba(17, 17, 19, 0.4));
    border: 1px solid var(--vf-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.25rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .quick-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .quick-card-body {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .quick-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--vf-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .quick-card-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--vf-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .quick-card-body p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--vf-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .quick-card-action {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--vf-green);
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .quick-card-action:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Grid Stack */
  .hub-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .hub-section-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .section-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--vf-text);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .heading-icon {
    color: var(--vf-text-tertiary);
  }

  .section-heading h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .cards-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .hub-card {
    background: var(--vf-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--vf-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-grow: 1;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .hub-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--vf-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .hub-card p {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--vf-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .card-link {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--vf-green);
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .hub-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .hub-card:hover .card-link {
    color: var(--vf-text);
  }

  /* Responsive styling */
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hub-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .quick-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 1.75rem;
    }
    .quick-card-action {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .docs-hub-hero {
      padding: 96px 1.25rem 4rem;
    }
    .hub-header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
